Description: Fix fullscreen toggle, window resize, and FBO at fixed resolution
 - Add toggleFullscreen() to Window using SDL_WINDOW_FULLSCREEN_DESKTOP (touche F)
 - Fix Window destructor to properly release SDL GL context and window
 - Fix Window::resize() to call SDL_SetWindowSize()
 - Remove duplicate uninitialised sdlWindow member from GLWindow
 - Add SDL event loop for SDL_QUIT and F key fullscreen toggle
 - Store FBO dimensions from settings so they stay fixed on resize/fullscreen
 - Fix gluPerspective aspect ratio (was integer division 1024/1024 = 1)
